        "op-heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "No surprises. That's the point.",
            "size": "6xl"
          }
        },
        "op-text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A renovation goes wrong in the gaps — between what was said and what was written, between what you expected and what showed up. Our process exists to close those gaps.</p>",
